## ‚öôÔ∏è Pin Map (ESP32 NodeMCU-32S)

| Component | Function | GPIO Pin |
|------------|-----------|-----------|
| Red LED | Output | 16 |
| Green LED | Output | 17 |
| Blue LED | Output | 18 |
| Mode Button | Input (Pull-up) | 32 |
| Reset Button | Input (Pull-up) | 33 |
| OLED SDA | I¬≤C Data | 21 |
| OLED SCL | I¬≤C Clock | 22 |
| OLED VCC | Power | 3.3V |
| OLED GND | Ground | GND |

